---
// Componente de Perfil Profesional y Stack Tecnológico
---

<section id="sobre-mi" class="py-24 px-6 relative bg-white/1">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
      {/* Columna de Texto: Biografía y Logros */}
      <div class="text-left">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-white">
          Un cuarto de siglo <br />
          <span class="text-blue-500 italic">evolucionando.</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-white/60 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Soy Licenciado en Administración con mención en Informática, egresado
          con honores <strong>CUM LAUDE</strong> de la Universidad Simón Rodríguez.
          Mi carrera comenzó en 1999 digitalizando sistemas para el sector ferroviario,
          y desde entonces he dedicado mi vida a fusionar la visión de negocios con
          la arquitectura técnica de vanguardia.
        </p>

        {/* Puntos clave del perfil */}
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
            >
              <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-blue-400"
                >workspace_premium</span
              >
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-bold">Excelencia Académica</h4>
              <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">
                Graduado Cum Laude, un reflejo del rigor y compromiso aplicado a
                cada proyecto.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
            >
              <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-emerald-400"
                >query_stats</span
              >
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-bold">Visión Híbrida</h4>
              <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">
                Capacidad única para traducir estados financieros y procesos de
                negocio en algoritmos eficientes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Estadísticas Rápidas */}
        <div class="flex gap-8 border-t border-white/5 pt-8">
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-white">25+</p>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">
              Años Exp
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-white">50+</p>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">
              Sistemas
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <a
              href="/sobre-mi"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-400 hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition-colors duration-200"
            >
              Saber más
              <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-blue-400 text-base">arrow_forward</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Columna de Skills: Stack Tecnológico */}
      <div class="glass-card p-10 rounded-[48px] relative border-white/5">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-8 text-white flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-blue-500">layers</span>
          Stack de Tecnologías
        </h3>

        <div class="space-y-10">
          {/* Backend & Arquitectura */}
          <div>
            <p
              class="text-[10px] font-bold text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4"
            >
              Arquitectura & Backend
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-blue-400 skill-badge"
                >node.js</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-blue-400 skill-badge"
                >VB.NET / C#</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-blue-400 skill-badge"
                >PHP</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-white/60 italic skill-badge"
                >VB 6.0 (Legacy Expert)</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Frontend Moderno */}
          <div>
            <p
              class="text-[10px] font-bold text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4"
            >
              Frontend Moderno
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-400 skill-badge"
                >Astro</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-400 skill-badge"
                >Tailwind CSS</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-400 skill-badge"
                >React</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-400 skill-badge"
                >JS</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Datos e Infraestructura */}
          <div>
            <p
              class="text-[10px] font-bold text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4"
            >
              Datos & Infraestructura
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-purple-400 skill-badge"
                >SQL Server</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-purple-400 skill-badge"
                >MySQL</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-purple-400 skill-badge"
                >SQLite</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Efecto de resplandor decorativo */}
        <div
          class="absolute -z-10 top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-600/5 blur-[100px] rounded-full"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
